[h1]Your pawns finally equip the right gear. Automatically.[/h1]

[b]Smart Gear[/b] analyzes each pawn's skills, traits, and ideology to detect their role. Based on role and current situation, it auto-equips the best available weapon, apparel, and supplies.

[b]Zero configuration.[/b] Works out of the box. Override per-pawn if you want control.

[hr][/hr]

[h1]Automatic Weapon Management[/h1]
[list]
[*] Colony-wide optimization -- best fighters get best weapons
[*] Hunting jobs auto-equip best ranged weapon
[*] Brawler trait = melee, high shooting = ranged
[*] Ideology weapon precepts and trait preferences respected
[/list]

[h1]Sidearms[/h1]
[list]
[*] Auto-picks up a secondary weapon (melee for shooters, ranged for brawlers)
[*] Auto-draws melee when attacked in close combat
[*] Restores primary weapon when undrafted
[/list]

[h1]Context-Aware Apparel[/h1]
[list]
[*] [b]Combat[/b]: armor and protection priority
[*] [b]Work[/b]: job-stat bonuses (medical gear for doctors)
[*] [b]Cold/Hot weather[/b]: insulation priority
[*] Nudist and ideology preferences respected
[*] Royal title requirements respected
[/list]

[h1]Inventory Management[/h1]
[list]
[*] Doctors auto-carry medicine (configurable count)
[/list]

[h1]Per-Pawn Control[/h1]
[list]
[*] Auto-detected role in Smart Gear tab
[*] Lock toggle to disable for specific pawns
[*] Manual role override
[*] Upgrade threshold prevents constant swapping
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h1]Roles[/h1]
[list]
[*] [b]Shooter[/b] -- High shooting, prefers ranged
[*] [b]Brawler[/b] -- High melee or Brawler trait
[*] [b]Doctor[/b] -- High medicine, medical gear, carries meds
[*] [b]Worker[/b] -- Low combat, work-stat clothing
[*] [b]Hunter[/b] -- Hunting job, long-range weapon
[*] [b]Pacifist[/b] -- Cannot do violence
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h1]Compatibility[/h1]
[list]
[*] Disable sidearms if using Simple Sidearms
[*] Safe to add or remove mid-save
[/list]

[h1]Requirements[/h1]
[list]
[*] RimWorld 1.6+
[*] [url=https://steamcommunity.com/workshop/filedetails/?id=2009463077]Harmony[/url]
[/list]

[hr][/hr]

[h1]Languages[/h1]
English, German, Chinese Simplified, Japanese, Korean, Russian, Spanish

